      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Teredo protocol defines a set of flags that are embedded in every Teredo IPv6 address.  This document specifies a set of security updates that modify the use of this flags field, but are backward compatible. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
